&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Strong understanding of HR processes and systems architecture, including integrations with other SaaS tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Demonstrated ability to experiment with and implement&lt;strong&gt; AI-driven or agentic systems&lt;/strong&gt;, automations, or chat-based tools within business workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
